reviews.review_text: You's Guys Rob's Excellent Recording Has Been Transferred Into A Near Board. Dried Lizards, Bat Wings, Whatever You Guys Are Doing'. Keep On Doing' It ! A Scarlet -> Fire For Ya. Who Don't Know Yet.

BEST OF THE AUDIENCE RECORDINGS! There are more than a dozen audience recordings of this fine concert. One of several that many claim to be the best was the early one uploaded in 2004, by R. Eaton. Now Charlie Miller has thrown his hat into the arena by upgrading that older show and given this version to us in 2022. 

From the first songs you can hear that this is one of the best non-Soundboard versions, but listen to  it more and you may agree that this new recording is (perhaps) now the best AUD we've got. Download it and listen, this is one of the hottest shows of that year, and this Scarlet > Fire is one of the top versions in the 80s. It's free, and though the soundboard is better, you can be satisfied with what you get with this new Charlie Miller upgrade!
